# 1. セカイの狭間で

Miku: Happy New Year!
Miku: It's great to see you so soon in the new year!
Miku: Yes, let's make this year wonderful too.
Miku: Thanks for looking after everyone with me last year. You were so helpful!
Miku: Thanks to you, I was also able to have an amazing year.
Miku: Would you be able to help me keep an eye on everyone this year too?
Miku: Yay! I was hoping you'd say that!
Miku: I hope this turns out to be another great year. For us here in SEKAI, for our friends from the real world, for everyone...
Miku: That includes you too, of course!
Miku: Oh, would you like to go over to SEKAI together?
Miku: I'm really curious to see how everyone's celebrating the New Year.
Miku: Great!
Miku: Let's go check up on everyone!
